# How to type Swedish characters using Ubuntu

source: [wikipedia]{https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_Unicode_characters}

| character | keyboard combination |
| --------- | -------------------- |
| å | CTRL + SHIFT + U + 00E5 |
| Å | CTRL + SHIFT + U + 00C5 |
| æ | CTRL + SHIFT + U + 00E6 |
| Æ | CTRL + SHIFT + U + 00C6 |
| ø | CTRL + SHIFT + U + 00F8 |
| Ø | CTRL + SHIFT + U + 00D8 |
